# 🗺️ WanderLust Project Audit

This is a complete functional and structural audit of the **WanderLust** full-stack travel platform.

## 1. Backend Implementation Status (Django / DRF)

### 🗄️ Models & Fields
**[User](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/models.py#29-56) (Custom AbstractBaseUser)**
- `email`: EmailField (unique)
- [role](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/serializers.py#36-40): CharField (Choices: USER, HOST, ADMIN, default: USER)
- `is_host_approved`: BooleanField (default: False)
- `is_staff`: BooleanField (default: False)
- `is_active`: BooleanField (default: True)
- `date_joined`: DateTimeField

**[Listing](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/models.py#6-33)**
- `host`: ForeignKey -> User (related_name: 'listings')
- `title`: CharField (max 200)
- `description`: TextField
- `price_per_night`: DecimalField (10, 2)
- `location`: CharField (max 255)
- `image`: URLField (max 500, blank=True, null=True)
- `rating`: DecimalField (3, 2, default: 0.00)
- `is_available`: BooleanField (default: True)
- `created_at`, `updated_at`: DateTimeFields

### 🔄 Serializers
- **[LoginSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/serializers.py#6-27)**: Handles email/password authentication & returns JWT tokens (`access`, `refresh`).
- **[RegisterSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/serializers.py#29-57)**: Validates registration, handles password hashing, sets [role](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/serializers.py#36-40). Approvals are flagged `False` automatically for HOST roles.
- **[ListingSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/serializers.py#4-19)**: Serializes all Listing fields; sets [id](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/serializers.py#10-27) and `created_at` as read-only.

### 🌐 API Endpoints & Routes Configured
**Users Routing (`api/users/` and root):**
- `/login/`, `/dashboard/`, `/create-listing/`, `/my-listings/` (Django Template Views)
- `/register/`, `/api-register/` (Register API)
- `/api-login/` (Login API)
- `/profile/` (Token Profile Info)
- `/token/refresh/` (JWT Refresh)
- `/admin/pending-hosts/` (Admin Host Applications)
- `/admin/approve-host/<int:user_id>/` (Admin Approve Host)

**Listings Routing (`api/listings/`):**
- `/create/` (POST - Create listing as approved Host)
- `/my/` (GET - Fetch listings belonging to logged-in user)
- `/featured/` (GET - Paginated, top-rated listings)

### 🧱 Views Created
- **APIView**: [RegisterView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#36-63), [LoginView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#67-73), [ProfileView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#76-84), [UserProfileView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#86-91), [PendingHostrequestView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#92-115), [HostDashboardView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#116-121), [ApproveHostView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#122-145), [AdminDashboardView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#147-152), [CreateListingView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/views.py#13-31), [MyListingView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/views.py#32-39)
- **Generics**: [FeaturedListingsView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/views.py#45-58) (ListAPIView)
- **Django Template Views (Basic)**: [login_page](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#22-26), [dashboard](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#27-29), [create_Listing_page](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#30-32), [my_listing_page](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/users/views.py#33-35)

### 📄 Pagination & Optimizations
- **Pagination**: Implemented [FeaturedListingPagination](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/views.py#40-44) (PageNumberPagination, default 6 items, max 20).
- **Optimization**: `select_related('host')` is used in [FeaturedListingsView](file:///c:/Users/Jhenkar/OneDrive/Desktop/Jhenkar/Project/wanderlust/listings/views.py#45-58) to prevent N+1 queries when fetching top-rated listings.

